              },
              "free_text": [
                " Intensities of strong",
                " 4214- and 4105-keV gamma rays in 23.4-eV thorium",
                " resonance measured relative to sum of intensities",
                " of gamma rays with energies exceeding 6.2 MeV in",
                " 4.9-eV resonance of gold in a separate experiment",
                " using composite thin samples of gold and thorium.",
                " Absolute intensities for gold taken from Kane.",
                "Relative number of neutrons captured in each resonance",
                " calculated from the measured relative neutron flux",
                " and the known resonance parameters using thorium",
                " values of Bhat and the gold parameters of Wood."
              ]
